<h3 class="t-sub-heading detail__sub-heading">In-depth how-tos</h3>
<p class="t-body detail__body">In addition to the UI video series, Build UX also offers how-to videos that dive deep into specific techniques and approaches for both product design and UX development. Examples of how-to video topics include advanced component structure in Figma, optimizing and implementing SVGs, and using CSS Grid and Custom Properties at the component level.</p>

