<h2 class="t-section-heading detail__section-heading">What&rsquo;s next</h2>
<p class="t-body detail__body">I&rsquo;m continuing to grow Build UX with frequent new video series and how-tos. My vision for Build UX is to always keep the core content both purchase-free and ad-free to reduce any barriers to access. There is no shortage of HTML, CSS, accessibility, design system, and product design topics to cover, so I&rsquo;m looking forward to many, many video to come!</p>
